Package: mcpr
Title: Model Context Protocol for R
Version: 0.0.2.9000
Authors@R: 
  c(
    person(given = "John",
           family = "Coene",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jcoenep@gmail.com"),
    person(family = "Opifex",
           role = c("cph", "fnd"),
           email = "john@opifex.org")
  )
Description: Create, run, and connect to Model Context Protocol (MCP) servers, and clients in R. The package
    provides a framework for implementing MCP-compatible servers with tools, 
    resources, and prompts capabilities, as well as client functionality to interact with
    MCP servers. It includes a JSON-RPC 2.0 implementation for communication between 
    clients and servers.
